snippet.title: Shootout At Old Tucson
snippet.description:
The Last game made from American Laser Games. Low Budget compare from its previous.
Only release on 3DO More like Lethal Enforcers with better frame rates.
Shootout at Old Tucson was also one of the first games by American Laser Games developed based on 3DO technology. But this Trailer is completely differs from the gameplay.
